            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2012%3A1-14%3A10%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%20Questions%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20always%20give%20me%20justice%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhen%20I%20bring%20a%20case%20before%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ESo%20let%20me%20bring%20you%20this%20complaint%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWhy%20are%20the%20wicked%20so%20prosperous%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWhy%20are%20evil%20people%20so%20happy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20planted%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20they%20have%20taken%20root%20and%20prospered.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYour%20name%20is%20on%20their%20lips%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20you%20are%20far%20from%20their%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20as%20for%20me%2C%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20know%20my%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYou%20see%20me%20and%20test%20my%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDrag%20these%20people%20away%20like%20sheep%20to%20be%20butchered!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ESet%20them%20aside%20to%20be%20slaughtered!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EHow%20long%20must%20this%20land%20mourn%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EEven%20the%20grass%20in%20the%20fields%20has%20withered.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20wild%20animals%20and%20birds%20have%20disappeared%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebecause%20of%20the%20evil%20in%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20the%20people%20have%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20see%20what%26%23x2019%3Bs%20ahead%20for%20us!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Reply%20to%20Jeremiah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20racing%20against%20mere%20men%20makes%20you%20tired%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehow%20will%20you%20race%20against%20horses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIf%20you%20stumble%20and%20fall%20on%20open%20ground%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhat%20will%20you%20do%20in%20the%20thickets%20near%20the%20Jordan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EEven%20your%20brothers%2C%20members%20of%20your%20own%20family%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehave%20turned%20against%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20plot%20and%20raise%20complaints%20against%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDo%20not%20trust%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eno%20matter%20how%20pleasantly%20they%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20abandoned%20my%20people%2C%20my%20special%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20have%20surrendered%20my%20dearest%20ones%20to%20their%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EMy%20chosen%20people%20have%20roared%20at%20me%20like%20a%20lion%20of%20the%20forest%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20I%20have%20treated%20them%20with%20contempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EMy%20chosen%20people%20act%20like%20speckled%20vultures%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Especkled%20hyenas.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20they%20themselves%20are%20surrounded%20by%20vultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBring%20on%20the%20wild%20animals%20to%20pick%20their%20corpses%20clean!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_12_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BMany%20rulers%20have%20ravaged%20my%20vineyard%2C%